14
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:42,570
“巫师号，莫比尔”
"Enchanter, Mobile."

15
00:02:45,660 --> 00:02:48,000
跑太远了吧
Well, we're a long way from home.

16
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,210
对他们鸣笛！
Wake them up!

17
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,550
是海军！
It's the Navy!

18
00:03:01,590 --> 00:03:03,510
快点，去拿国旗！
Quick, put out the flag!

19
