备忘录
memos,

345
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:43,960
信件
letters,

346
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:45,070
信用卡帐单
credit card statements...

347
00:21:45,150 --> 00:21:47,080
还有私人税单
And we got personal income tax,

348
00:21:47,150 --> 00:21:49,730
- 公司税单…  - 话费单、公司章程
- corporate income tax... - phone bills, article of incorporation.

349
