你破解密码所需的全部资料
Everything you could need to break his code.

350
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:52,710
这是什么？
What's... What's this?

351
00:21:53,860 --> 00:21:54,980
国中毕业纪念册
Old high school yearbook.

352
00:21:55,140 --> 00:21:56,890
女朋友、足球队
Sweethearts, football team.

353
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:58,780
有用吗？
You think?

354
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,610
我不知道
I don't know.

355
00:22:00,690 --> 00:22:03,320
好吧，我们来试试看吧
Okay, let's see what we've got here.

356
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:06,650
- 没加奶精  - 没加奶精
- No cream. - There wasn't any cream.

357
00:22:07,360 --> 00:22:09,490
人们最爱用生日日期，就从这个试起吧
People are big on birthdays. Let's start there.

358
00:22:09,570 --> 00:22:11,320
我猜你的提款卡密码也是你的生日日期
I'll bet your ATM code is your birthday.

359
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:12,280
差不多
Close.

360
00:22:12,370 --> 00:22:13,830
顺序颠倒吗？
In reverse?

361
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,210
好了，他的生日是…
All right, his birthday is...

362
00:22:20,210 --> 00:22:21,790
真简单，不是吗？
That'd be too easy, wouldn't it?

363
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:24,280
试试顺序颠倒
Let's try it in reverse.

364
00:22:24,380 --> 00:22:25,550
（使用者哈丁的密码 04-12-4密码无效）

365
