埃内斯托
Ernesto?

682
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:56,610
你认为在我把美国那家人干掉后
You think one of the others is trying to ruin me,

683
00:42:56,740 --> 00:42:59,360
有人想毁了我，抢我的生意？
to steal my business, after what I did to the American?

684
00:42:59,450 --> 00:43:03,450
我猜也不是你想的那样
I guess that wasn't quite the deterrent you thought it would be.

685
00:43:05,160 --> 00:43:06,950
去查出是谁
Find out who it is.

686
00:43:15,090 --> 00:43:16,930
你怎么看这件事，上校？
What do you make of this, Colonel?

687
00:43:19,260 --> 00:43:20,800
一个机会
An opportunity.

688
