00:43:48,570 --> 00:43:49,580
抱歉迟到了
I'm sorry I'm late.

694
00:43:49,660 --> 00:43:51,040
我有十分钟
I got 10 minutes.

695
00:43:52,330 --> 00:43:53,500
好的
Okay.

696
