It's definitely drug money.

698
00:43:58,880 --> 00:44:00,970
但你无法证明
But you can't prove it.

699
00:44:01,050 --> 00:44:02,340
目前是的
So far.

700
00:44:04,300 --> 00:44:05,870
介意我问你一个问题吗？
Mind if I ask you a question?

701
00:44:06,430 --> 00:44:07,180
不会
No.

702
00:44:08,140 --> 00:44:10,140
为什么告诉我这件事？
Why are you telling me all this?

703
00:44:10,230 --> 00:44:12,690
