As you can imagine, he and his team are pretty busy at the moment.

837
00:52:51,000 --> 00:52:53,580
（林度咖啡）

838
00:52:59,840 --> 00:53:00,700
不，不
No, no.

839
00:53:00,920 --> 00:53:03,090
必须避开这条街
This avenue has to be avoided.

840
