They'll be coming from the airport...

841
00:53:05,220 --> 00:53:07,140
沿厄尔多拉多大道
up Avenida Aeropuerto El Dorado

842
00:53:07,220 --> 00:53:09,260
到阿美利亚大道
all the way to Gran America.

843
00:53:09,350 --> 00:53:11,220
圣大非是我们的据点
Santa Fe's our spot.

844
00:53:12,390 --> 00:53:14,560
我很想留在这里看好戏
As much as I would love to be here for this,

845
00:53:14,690 --> 00:53:17,310
但我得到华盛顿办点事
I have to take care of some business in Washington,

846
00:53:17,400 --> 00:53:19,520
有些事要做了结
tying up some loose ends.

847
00:53:29,370 --> 00:53:31,450
喂，别挂断！别挂断！
Hello. Don't hang up! Don't hang up!

848
00:53:31,540 --> 00:53:32,620
拜
Bye.

849
00:53:34,580 --> 00:53:35,670
喂？
Hello?

850
00:53:35,750 --> 00:53:37,210
答录机还开着，莫伊拉
The machine is still on, Moira.

851
