The smoke will give us cover. It's our only chance.

899
01:00:56,560 --> 01:00:58,440
我背他
I got him.

900
01:00:58,520 --> 01:01:00,280
冲向驾驶座
Make for the driver's side.

901
01:01:00,360 --> 01:01:01,650
预备…走！
Ready? Go!

902
01:01:12,200 --> 01:01:13,370
进去！
Get in!

903
01:01:13,500 --> 01:01:14,830
快走！快走！
Go! Go!

904
