Don't tell me you're in this thing.

914
01:03:02,440 --> 01:03:04,780
我就在现场
I'm right in the middle of it.

915
01:03:05,110 --> 01:03:06,850
亲爱的，丹恩死了
Honey, Dan was killed.

916
01:03:07,060 --> 01:03:07,950
丹恩·穆雷
Dan Murray.

917
01:03:11,620 --> 01:03:14,830
我近在咫尺却束手无策
I was 10 feet away. There was nothing I could do.

918
01:03:17,500 --> 01:03:19,040
我要回家了
I'm coming home.

919
01:03:19,120 --> 01:03:20,370
谢天谢地
Thank God.

920
01:03:20,460 --> 01:03:21,830
我爱你
I love you.

921
01:03:28,010 --> 01:03:30,220
我以为没人知道他去那里
I thought his going down there was a secret.

922
01:03:30,300 --> 01:03:31,430
是的
It was.

923
01:03:31,510 --> 01:03:33,180
那么我不明白
Then I don't get it.

924
01:03:33,300 --> 01:03:34,390
怎么会这样？
What happened?

925
01:03:34,570 --> 01:03:36,220
没人知道
Nobody knows.

926
01:03:36,310 --> 01:03:38,930
这些人怎么这么蠢？
How stupid are these people?

927
01:03:39,020 --> 01:03:40,900
他们认为可以为所欲为
They believe they can do anything.

928
01:03:40,980 --> 01:03:43,190
知道吗？他们错了
You know what? They're wrong.

929
01:03:44,190 --> 01:03:46,190
- 是，总统  - 大错特错
- Yes, sir. - They're wrong.

930
01:03:48,360 --> 01:03:49,650
他们公然挑战
They've directly challenged

931
01:03:49,740 --> 01:03:52,490
美国政府的公权力
the sovereign power of the United States.

932
01:03:54,530 --> 01:03:57,120
不能再通讯息了
No more sending messages.

933
01:03:57,200 --> 01:04:00,490
不管电话有没有响，他要他们全面监控
He wants them to get the message whether the phone rings or not.

934
01:04:01,500 --> 01:04:03,420
他下的令吗？
Those are his words?

935
01:04:03,500 --> 01:04:05,710
听来像吗？
Do they sound like his words?

936
01:04:06,550 --> 01:04:10,590
