I wish I had done it. They deserve it.

943
01:04:38,720 --> 01:04:40,060
但不是我干的
But it wasn't me.

944
01:04:40,370 --> 01:04:41,870
那么是谁干的？
Who did, then?

945
01:04:43,580 --> 01:04:47,380
你总是没答案
You know, you have no answers.

946
01:04:49,590 --> 01:04:52,840
