1137
01:17:48,700 --> 01:17:52,290
遇害者的姓名有没有可能是假名？
Any chances any of these bombing victims' names are aliases?

1138
01:17:52,370 --> 01:17:54,710
不可能 所有身分都查证过了
No. All IDs have been confirmed.

1139
01:17:55,670 --> 01:17:56,920
你想找谁？
Who were you hoping for?

1140
01:17:57,000 --> 01:17:58,880
他不在名单里 柯特斯不在名单里
He's not here, he's not here. Cortez.

1141
01:17:59,000 --> 01:18:00,500
他不在名单里
He's not here.

1142
01:18:03,090 --> 01:18:05,720
行动小组为什么要副本？
Why was Operations copied on this?

1143
01:18:05,840 --> 01:18:07,550
里特要求的
Ritter requested it.

1144
01:18:08,430 --> 01:18:10,140
里特？
Ritter, huh?

1145
01:18:10,220 --> 01:18:12,310
你今天很漂亮
You look very nice today.

1146
01:18:12,390 --> 01:18:13,730
谢谢
Thank you.

1147
01:18:28,200 --> 01:18:29,410
汽车炸弹
Car bomb.

1148
01:18:39,420 --> 01:18:42,000
汽车炸弹点燃会怎样？
What happens when a car bomb goes off?

1149
01:18:42,090 --> 01:18:43,210
会炸开
It explodes.

1150
01:18:43,300 --> 01:18:45,420
对，会向外炸开
Right. It blows up and out.

1151
01:18:46,260 --> 01:18:47,760
导弹呢？
And a missile?

1152
01:18:52,100 --> 01:18:54,390
- 像这种比较深的坑洞？  - 那是导弹的特性
- This deep a crater? - That's characteristic.

1153
01:18:54,810 --> 01:18:57,270
现在看看卫星图片
Okay, bring up the satellite photo.

1154
01:19:03,480 --> 01:19:05,940
是HMX和TNT
HMX and TNT

1155
01:19:07,070 --> 01:19:08,780
用七比三的比例混合
which when you mix it 70-30,

1156
01:19:08,840 --> 01:19:10,780
能制造出所谓的奥托尔化合物
you get a compound called Octol.

1157
01:19:10,910 --> 01:19:12,490
在后车箱放足够的量
Put enough explosives in the back of a car

1158
01:19:12,580 --> 01:19:13,760
就会炸出那么大的坑洞
and you'll get a crater that big.

1159
01:19:13,880 --> 01:19:14,860
它很稳定
It's very stable,

1160
01:19:14,920 --> 01:19:16,840
- 对，但车子还会在里头吗？ - 很昂贵…
- Yeah, but would it still be in it? - very expensive...

1161
01:19:16,910 --> 01:19:18,670
管它什么车的，它还会在坑洞里头吗？
The car, the truck, whatever, would it still be in the crater?

1162
01:19:18,750 --> 01:19:20,710
- 爆炸威力强大  - 我想车子会炸成碎片
- Very violent. - I think it would be blown to bits.

1163
01:19:20,790 --> 01:19:22,750
这边到处都会有它的碎片
There'd be pieces of it all around there.

1164
01:19:22,840 --> 01:19:25,590
哪里生产奥托尔？
And where is Octol made?

1165
01:19:25,670 --> 01:19:26,960
很多地方都有
Lots of places.

1166
01:19:27,220 --> 01:19:28,150
欧洲
Europe,

1167
01:19:28,470 --> 01:19:29,490
美国
the US.

1168
01:19:29,800 --> 01:19:31,540
但没人使用
But nobody uses it.

1169
01:19:31,930 --> 01:19:34,560
除了军方没人负担得起
Nobody can afford it except the military.

1170
01:19:34,640 --> 01:19:37,060
空中轰炸做得到
An aerial bomb would do that,

1171
01:19:37,140 --> 01:19:40,060
不过这不是空中轰炸
but that's not an aerial bomb.

1172
01:19:40,150 --> 01:19:41,650
- 不是吗？  - 不是
- It's not? - No.

1173
01:19:41,770 --> 01:19:44,860
所有东西都有纤维残留物
There is also a cellulose residue on everything.

1174
01:19:45,440 --> 01:19:48,160
这里和这里应该都要有炸弹碎片
There should be shrapnel here and here...

1175
01:19:48,620 --> 01:19:49,490
可是却没有
but there isn't.

1176
01:19:50,660 --> 01:19:52,320
没有炸弹碎片
No bomb fragments.

1177
01:20:00,670 --> 01:20:03,130
（国际防御指南 部队武器大全）

1178
01:20:19,680 --> 01:20:20,690
（化合军用武器）

1179
01:20:33,530 --> 01:20:36,370
（纤维料雷射导弹）

1180
01:20:36,370 --> 01:20:39,370
“纤维料雷射导弹”
"Cellulose encased laser-guided bomb."

1181
01:20:43,000 --> 01:20:44,170
文件
Paper.

1182
01:20:48,840 --> 01:20:50,720
美国人做的
The Americans are here.

1183
01:21:21,290 --> 01:21:23,710
我们有共同点
We have something in common.

1184
01:21:23,790 --> 01:21:25,750
我们不能执行政策
Neither of us can implement policy

1185
01:21:25,880 --> 01:21:29,920
至少没有雇主的默许
without at least tacit authorization from our employer.

1186
01:21:30,050 --> 01:21:32,010
另外还有一个共同点
We have something else in common.

1187
01:21:32,090 --> 01:21:35,180
我们俩都知道美军在哥伦比亚
We both know there are American troops in Colombia

1188
01:21:35,260 --> 01:21:37,390
展开一场非法之战
fighting an illegal war.

1189
01:21:39,220 --> 01:21:41,350
星期三我会在巴拿马市
I will be staying at the Hotel Paloma de Oro

1190
01:21:41,430 --> 01:21:43,560
派洛玛欧洛饭店
in Panama City on Wednesday.

1191
01:21:44,440 --> 01:21:46,100
我提议见个面
I suggest we meet.

1192
01:22:38,360 --> 01:22:40,370
小六，我是小尖，结束
Six, this is Point. Over.

1193
01:22:41,660 --> 01:22:42,990
我是小六
Six here.

1194
01:22:43,870 --> 01:22:46,000
毒品在这里，数量很多
The stuff's here and there's a lot of it.

1195
01:22:46,120 --> 01:22:50,290
还有一百到一百五十名
I'm also looking at 100 to 150 men,

1196
01:22:50,380 --> 01:22:52,920
持枪的人，好像在等什么
armed, waiting around for something.

1197
01:22:53,000 --> 01:22:54,260
结束
Over.

1198
01:22:54,340 --> 01:22:56,170
哥伦比亚军吗？结束
Colombian Army? Over.

1199
01:23:00,640 --> 01:23:02,890
不是，看来像佣兵
Negative. They look like mercenaries.

1200
01:23:02,970 --> 01:23:04,020
结束
Over.

1201
01:23:04,140 --> 01:23:05,680
好的
All right.

1202
01:23:05,810 --> 01:23:07,770
撤退，终止任务
Get on back here. Abort mission.

1203
01:23:07,850 --> 01:23:10,190
重复，终止任务，通话结束
I say again, abort mission. Out.

1204
01:23:12,480 --> 01:23:14,190
一百五十名持枪的人？
150 armed men, huh?

1205
01:23:16,150 --> 01:23:18,820
（最高机密）

1206
01:23:35,880 --> 01:23:37,880
麻烦双手举高
Raise your arms, please.

1207
01:23:53,520 --> 01:23:56,690
谢谢你这么快回覆
Thank you for responding to my note so promptly.

1208
01:23:58,440 --> 01:24:02,320
你应该知道我跟雅各布斯先生的死无关
You should know that I had nothing to do with the death of Mr. Jacobs.

1209
01:24:02,410 --> 01:24:04,120
这是疯子所为
It was an act of madness,

1210
01:24:04,200 --> 01:24:07,040
不过是我的众多雇主里最疯狂的一个
but a typical one from the men I work for.

1211
01:24:08,870 --> 01:24:10,500
你想要什么？
What do you want?

1212
01:24:10,580 --> 01:24:12,710
跟你一样，矿泉水
Same as you. Mineral water.

1213
01:24:13,380 --> 01:24:16,750
我们都同意只要美国人有毒品的需求
Can we agree that as long as Americans demand drugs,

1214
01:24:16,880 --> 01:24:18,670
就会有人想卖吧？
someone will supply them?

1215
01:24:18,760 --> 01:24:21,340
听好，非必要的话，我不想在此久留
Look, I don't want to be here any longer than I have to.

1216
01:24:21,430 --> 01:24:23,390
你在传真函里提到非法之战
You said something in your fax about a gang war.

1217
01:24:23,470 --> 01:24:25,050
什么意思？
What does that mean?

1218
01:24:25,140 --> 01:24:27,640
你和我要的都一样
That you and I want the same thing.

1219
01:24:27,720 --> 01:24:29,810
一样吗？
"The same thing." Really?

1220
01:24:29,890 --> 01:24:32,020
只是目前，全都是你在做
Only so far, you've done all the work.

1221
01:24:32,100 --> 01:24:34,900
你解决了那几条小鱼
You've taken care of the little fish.

1222
01:24:34,980 --> 01:24:37,820
我来解决漏网那条大鱼
I will take care of the one that got away.

1223
01:24:37,900 --> 01:24:39,780
一旦铲除了埃斯科贝多
Once Escobedo is gone,

1224
01:24:40,740 --> 01:24:42,910
我就可以顺理成章地帮你
I will be in the position to help you.

1225
01:24:42,990 --> 01:24:44,620
你要帮我？
You want to help me, huh?

1226
01:24:44,740 --> 01:24:47,290
帮你的国家、你的人民
Your country, your people.

1227
01:24:47,410 --> 01:24:50,250
藉由重新协定毒品交易
By restructuring the drug trade,

1228
01:24:50,330 --> 01:24:51,960
将它规则化
by regulating it.

1229
01:24:53,580 --> 01:24:55,040
如果我跟你保证
What would you say if I promised you

1230
01:24:55,130 --> 01:24:58,920
可卡因输入美国的量减半呢？
I will reduce the cocaine shipments to your country by half?

1231
01:25:00,670 --> 01:25:03,970
我想你一定吸毒吸到头壳坏了
I'd say you've been using too much of your product.

1232
01:25:05,010 --> 01:25:08,720
我也可以跟你保证常常破获大宗案件
I can also promise you regular quotas on major arrests

1233
01:25:08,810 --> 01:25:11,430
你的警方可以立功
that your police can take credit for.

1234
01:25:12,140 --> 01:25:14,480
想像一下：破案率大增
Imagine that, dramatic seizures,

1235
01:25:14,600 --> 01:25:17,650
毒品锐减，再也没有无谓的暴力事件
drastic reductions, no more senseless violence.

1236
01:25:18,610 --> 01:25:20,610
你会取得胜利
You'll have your victory.

1237
01:25:25,320 --> 01:25:27,120
代价是什么？
In return for what?

1238
01:25:28,160 --> 01:25:30,500
我也需要功绩
Well, I also need a victory

1239
01:25:30,620 --> 01:25:33,500
才能在残余的犯罪集团里建立我的地位
to establish my position with what is left of the cartel

1240
01:25:34,170 --> 01:25:36,670
如此才能帮你
so I can help you.

1241
01:25:37,630 --> 01:25:41,510
我必须打败那些到处乱炸的士兵
I need to defeat those soldiers blowing up everything they see.

1242
01:25:42,510 --> 01:25:45,430
给我他们的位置图
Give me maps of their locations.

1243
01:25:45,510 --> 01:25:47,720
切断他们的通讯
Cut off their communications.

1244
01:25:55,480 --> 01:25:59,020
缉毒署把监控录音带寄过来
DEA is sending the audio surveillance tape.

1245
01:25:59,860 --> 01:26:01,650
我还没收到
I haven't got it yet.

1246
01:26:03,990 --> 01:26:05,910
你可知道躺在这里…
You know what you think about

1247
01:26:07,200 --> 01:26:08,830
会有什么想法吗？
when you're lying here?

1248
01:26:10,580 --> 01:26:13,330
知道自己快死了，心里想…
You know you're gonna die, and you think

1249
01:26:15,710 --> 01:26:17,420
没关系的
that's all right.

1250
01:26:17,500 --> 01:26:19,380
你已经活够久了
You lived a long time.

1251
01:26:20,550 --> 01:26:23,050
你有爱你的家人
You had a family that loved you.

1252
01:26:23,170 --> 01:26:27,010
也有一份自以为能改变一切的工作
You had a job that you thought made a difference,

1253
01:26:28,340 --> 01:26:30,680
以为这是很光荣的…
that you thought was honorable.

1254
01:26:32,180 --> 01:26:34,020
…结果却看到这些
And then you see this.

1255
01:26:38,900 --> 01:26:41,230
我怕再追查下去
I'm afraid if I dig any deeper,

1256
01:26:42,900 --> 01:26:45,400
没有人会喜欢我发现的真相
no one's gonna like what I find.

1257
01:26:51,410 --> 01:26:53,200
你发过誓…
You took an oath,

1258
01:26:54,790 --> 01:26:56,410
…如果你记得…
if you recall,

1259
01:26:59,960 --> 01:27:02,590
就在你第一天来替我工作的时候
when you first came to work for me,

1260
01:27:03,420 --> 01:27:06,840
我不是指
and I don't mean to the National Security Advisor

1261
01:27:06,920 --> 01:27:08,760
美国国家安全顾问
of the United States.

1262
01:27:10,430 --> 01:27:12,220
我是指他的老板
I mean to his boss.

1263
01:27:13,890 --> 01:27:16,230
我也不是指总统
And I don't mean the President.

1264
01:27:18,100 --> 01:27:20,770
你对他的老板…
You gave your word to

1265
01:27:23,070 --> 01:27:24,440
发过誓
his boss.

1266
01:27:25,650 --> 01:27:31,820
你对美国人民发过誓
You gave your word to the people of the United States.

1267
01:27:34,290 --> 01:27:36,290
发过誓就要实现
Your word is who you are.

1268
01:27:42,420 --> 01:27:44,420
你还带了什么？
What else you got there?

1269
01:27:49,930 --> 01:27:52,300
我带了几本新杂志给你
I brought you some new magazines.

1270
01:28:02,770 --> 01:28:06,690
东帝汶的局势似乎稳定下来了
...and the situation in East Timor seems to have stabilized during the day.

1271
01:28:06,780 --> 01:28:07,860
很好
Good.

1272
01:28:08,610 --> 01:28:09,820
就这样吗？
Is that it?

1273
01:28:09,950 --> 01:28:11,990
还有一件事
Except for the other thing.

1274
01:28:13,990 --> 01:28:17,080
我们做得很成功，也看到具体成果
We've accomplished a lot. We're seeing tangible results.

1275
01:28:17,160 --> 01:28:18,220
毒品运量减少
Drug shipments are down.

1276
01:28:18,290 --> 01:28:19,830
黑市价格上升
Price on the street is rising.

1277
01:28:20,870 --> 01:28:24,670
看来政府的行动是正确的
Perception is that the administration is doing something right.

1278
01:28:25,630 --> 01:28:27,380
坏消息呢？
What's the bad news?

1279
01:28:30,550 --> 01:28:32,930
我担心最近这起
I'm concerned about this latest incident,

1280
01:28:33,010 --> 01:28:36,560
汽车炸弹案，紧接着雅各布斯遇刺案发生
the car bomb coming so soon after Jacobs' assassination.

1281
01:28:37,970 --> 01:28:40,600
让记者有文章可做
It's just the kind of thing reporters live for.

1282
01:28:40,690 --> 01:28:42,810
他们最爱把事件做连结
They'd love to try to make a connection.

1283
01:28:42,900 --> 01:28:44,860
你认为他们会
And you think they will.

1284
01:28:46,520 --> 01:28:49,400
我认为是该做个了断了
I think it's time the whole thing went away.

1285
01:28:50,650 --> 01:28:52,070
如果你是这么想的话
If that's what you think.

1286
01:28:52,150 --> 01:28:53,530
我是这么想
I think so.

1287
01:28:56,240 --> 01:28:58,410
那么就做个了断吧
Then it should go away.

1288
01:28:58,490 --> 01:29:00,160
当作从没发生过
It never happened.

1289
01:29:02,210 --> 01:29:03,500
是的，总统
Yes, sir.

1290
01:29:05,580 --> 01:29:08,420
是有可能
Well, I mean, it's possible.

1291
01:29:09,380 --> 01:29:10,720
如果能告诉我
It would be a lot easier

1292
01:29:10,840 --> 01:29:14,800
你要我入侵哪个系统，会比较简单点
if you told me whose system you wanted me to break into.

1293
01:29:14,890 --> 01:29:17,260
- 早安，莱恩博士  - 早安
- Good morning, Dr. Ryan. - Morning.

1294
01:29:38,370 --> 01:29:40,240
这不光是生日日期而已
We're way beyond birthdays now.

1295
01:29:42,120 --> 01:29:45,370
我必须写个特别的程式
I'm gonna have to write a special program here.

1296
01:29:48,920 --> 01:29:50,130
好的
Right.

1297
01:29:57,390 --> 01:30:00,720
好了，宝贝，开始工作吧
Okay, sweetheart, let's get to work.

1298
01:30:02,220 --> 01:30:03,730
很好
Fine. Good.

1299
01:30:05,440 --> 01:30:06,560
太好了！
Yes!

1300
01:30:07,940 --> 01:30:09,480
开始罗
Here we go.

1301
01:30:49,610 --> 01:30:52,150
（422号使用者登入）

1302
01:31:06,370 --> 01:31:08,960
“互惠行动”那是什么？
"Reciprocity." What's that?

1303
01:31:21,720 --> 01:31:22,760
喂
Yeah.

1304
01:31:22,850 --> 01:31:24,100
我忘了告诉你
I forgot to tell you.

1305
01:31:24,180 --> 01:31:25,390
取得密码后
After you get the code,

1306
01:31:25,470 --> 01:31:28,480
等他登出系统，你再登入
wait until he's off his system before you log on

1307
01:31:28,560 --> 01:31:30,440
不然他会发现你入侵
because he will know it when you do.

1308
01:31:30,520 --> 01:31:32,360
老天，太迟了
Jesus, Petey, it's too late.

1309
01:31:32,980 --> 01:31:34,150
哦，我的天
Oh, my God.

1310
01:31:47,160 --> 01:31:48,500
（小型步兵团 突袭哥伦比亚）

1311
01:31:48,660 --> 01:31:49,830
（人员伤亡）

1312
01:31:50,000 --> 01:31:51,170
（歼灭）

1313
01:31:54,840 --> 01:31:57,210
（删除）
（删除档案名称：互惠01）

1314
01:32:06,060 --> 01:32:07,680
（发文者：卡特）

1315
01:32:07,720 --> 01:32:08,730
卡特
Cutter.

1316
01:32:08,890 --> 01:32:10,230
（档案已删除）

1317
01:32:21,700 --> 01:32:22,870
喂
Yeah.

1318
01:32:22,950 --> 01:32:25,120
巴伯，我是杰克·莱恩
Bob, Jack Ryan here.

1319
01:32:25,200 --> 01:32:27,290
早安，杰克
Good morning, Jack.

1320
01:32:27,370 --> 01:32:28,800
早安，我只是在想
Morning. Listen, I was just thinking,

1321
01:32:28,880 --> 01:32:31,120
我们刚开始对彼此印象不好
maybe we got off to a bad start here.

1322
01:32:31,250 --> 01:32:33,670
既然要在这里合作
We're going to be working together here.

1323
01:32:34,040 --> 01:32:36,670
或许该花点时间多多了解彼此
Maybe we should spend some time. Get to know each other a little better.

1324
01:32:36,750 --> 01:32:38,550
你打网球吗？
You play tennis?

1325
