01:48:15,480 --> 01:48:16,900
一架直升机
A helicopter.

1513
01:48:26,700 --> 01:48:28,200
不，谢了
No, thank you.

1514
01:48:30,750 --> 01:48:32,330
现在怎样，快乐时光吗？
What is this, happy hour?

1515
01:48:32,430 --> 01:48:33,790
天天都是快乐时光
It's always happy hour.

1516
01:48:34,170 --> 01:48:35,640
这家店是你的机师的？
Your pilot owns this joint?

1517
01:48:35,730 --> 01:48:37,050
他住这里
He lives here.

1518
01:48:43,390 --> 01:48:44,890
就是他
Here he is.

1519
01:48:56,070 --> 01:48:58,070
- 早安  - 早安
- Good morning. - Good morning.

1520
01:48:58,190 --> 01:49:00,900
早安，我想租直升机
Good morning, I'm here to rent the Huey.

1521
01:49:01,030 --> 01:49:03,410
抱歉，直升机不出租
Sorry. We don't rent it anymore,

1522
01:49:03,530 --> 01:49:05,240
但有出售
but it is for sale.

1523
01:49:07,370 --> 01:49:08,910
多少钱？
How much is it?

1524
01:49:10,250 --> 01:49:11,580
两百万元
$2 million.

1525
01:49:18,300 --> 01:49:20,800
机师和我想试飞看看
My pilot and I would have to take it for a test flight.

1526
01:49:20,880 --> 01:49:24,050
当然好，付订金就行了
Yes, of course. You just have to leave a deposit.

1527
01:49:26,050 --> 01:49:27,850
要付多少？
How much is that?

1528
01:49:27,930 --> 01:49:29,310
两百万元
$2 million.

1529
01:49:35,310 --> 01:49:37,610
你收不收公司支票？
Would you take a company check?

1530
01:49:41,070 --> 01:49:43,150
（杰克·莱恩 情报局副局长）

1531
01:49:45,110 --> 01:49:46,240
收
Yes.

1532
01:49:54,620 --> 01:49:55,520
给你吧
Here we go.

1533
01:49:55,600 --> 01:49:57,960
真是他妈的大啊，不是吗？
She's a big son of a bitch, ain't she?

1534
01:50:00,590 --> 01:50:03,170
你何时飞过这型直升机？
You have any time in this type?

1535
01:50:03,260 --> 01:50:04,510
九点的时候
9:00.

1536
01:50:14,770 --> 01:50:16,400
离开我的直升机
Get out of my chopper.

1537
01:50:16,480 --> 01:50:19,400
不、不，这是我的直升机
No, no, no. My chopper.

1538
01:50:19,480 --> 01:50:20,940
起飞吧
Let's go.

1539
01:50:41,630 --> 01:50:45,170
最后一次通讯在这里
Their last communication put them here.

1540
01:50:46,150 --> 01:50:49,800
最近的撤退点在这里
The closest extraction point is here,

1541
01:50:50,080 --> 01:50:51,180
在这峡谷里
in this gorge.

1542
01:50:51,970 --> 01:50:53,220
知道了
I got it.

1543
01:51:13,490 --> 01:51:15,500
那是尸体吗？
Is that a body down there?

1544
01:51:16,210 --> 01:51:17,540
是的
Yeah.

1545
01:51:19,000 --> 01:51:20,500
我们的人吗？
One of ours?

1546
01:51:21,040 --> 01:51:22,500
我的人
One of mine.

1547
01:51:25,920 --> 01:51:28,430
找个地方降落
Find a place to set her down.

1548
01:51:28,510 --> 01:51:30,550
我们去找其他人
We'll look for the others.

1549
01:52:13,970 --> 01:52:15,720
无处可逃
Nowhere to run to.

1550
01:52:17,270 --> 01:52:18,680
无处可藏
No place to hide.

1551
01:52:18,770 --> 01:52:20,730
到处都是血渍
Blood trails everywhere.

1552
01:52:21,560 --> 01:52:23,610
全都引往河边
They all lead to the river.

1553
01:52:37,410 --> 01:52:40,120
这是我们从空中看到的瀑布
These are the falls we saw from the air.

1554
01:52:41,580 --> 01:52:44,130
尸体应该在下游50公尺
They should be about 50 meters down.

1555
01:52:57,140 --> 01:52:58,610
你抛下了我们！
You left us!

1556
01:52:58,800 --> 01:53:02,270
你抛下了我们，完全没支援！
You left us with no support at all!

1557
01:53:02,350 --> 01:53:05,400
你抛下我们自生自灭，混蛋…
Clark, you left us out to dry! You son of a...

1558
01:53:05,480 --> 01:53:07,900
冷静！冷静！冷静，小子！
Easy, easy, son! Easy, ease up, son!

1559
01:53:07,980 --> 01:53:09,820
放开！
Get off!

1560
01:53:09,940 --> 01:53:11,780
这不是他的错！
It's not his fault!

1561
01:53:11,860 --> 01:53:13,610
那是谁的错？！
Whose fault is it?

1562
01:53:15,030 --> 01:53:16,530
是我的错
It's my fault.

1563
01:53:21,830 --> 01:53:23,330
是我的错
It's my fault.

1564
01:53:36,180 --> 01:53:39,720
我离最后一次攻击地点
I was on point when the last attack came,

1565
01:53:41,140 --> 01:53:42,810
一哩多远
over a mile away.

1566
01:53:44,520 --> 01:53:47,060
等我赶回去时，一切都结束了
By the time I got back, it was over.

1567
01:53:48,320 --> 01:53:50,820
他们带走了队长欧索
They were taking the captain and Oso.

1568
01:53:52,570 --> 01:53:53,990
其他人呢？
The others?

1569
01:53:55,360 --> 01:53:56,870
被我埋了
I buried them.

1570
01:54:06,040 --> 01:54:07,710
那条路通往城里
Road to the town.

1571
01:54:08,340 --> 01:54:10,340
他们在这里载走俘虏
They loaded the prisoners here.

1572
01:54:10,420 --> 01:54:11,710
血渍斑斑
Blood everywhere.

1573
01:54:11,840 --> 01:54:14,010
天知道他们此刻在哪
God knows where they are now.

1574
01:54:14,090 --> 01:54:15,720
埃斯科贝多知道
Escobedo knows.

1575
01:54:15,840 --> 01:54:16,920
你打算怎么做
What are you going to do,

1576
01:54:17,050 --> 01:54:18,350
敲他家门吗？
knock on his door?

1577
01:54:25,770 --> 01:54:26,710
早安
Good morning.

1578
01:54:26,900 --> 01:54:28,580
我想见埃内斯托·埃斯科贝多
I'd like to see Ernesto Escobedo.

1579
01:54:28,670 --> 01:54:30,570
没有事先预约
I don't have an appointment.

1580
01:54:44,370 --> 01:54:45,710
好吧
Okay.

1581
01:54:48,250 --> 01:54:49,540
双手举起来
Arms up.

1582
01:54:50,880 --> 01:54:52,090
双手举起来！
Arms up!

1583
01:55:01,260 --> 01:55:03,060
是录音机
It's a tape recorder.

1584
01:55:07,440 --> 01:55:08,650
他进去了
He's in.

1585
01:55:12,650 --> 01:55:15,110
小鸟，这是变数，请回答
Bird, this is Variable. Over.

1586
01:55:17,490 --> 01:55:20,240
小鸟，这是变数，请回答
Bird, this is Variable. Over.

1587
01:55:37,340 --> 01:55:38,630
莱恩博士
Dr. Ryan.

1588
01:55:39,840 --> 01:55:41,100
请进
Come in.

1589
01:55:55,110 --> 01:55:56,320
请坐
Sit down.

1590
01:55:57,110 --> 01:55:58,990
有什么我能效劳的？
What can I do for you?

1591
01:56:00,280 --> 01:56:02,990
我不知道还能找谁
Well, I didn't know who else to turn to.

1592
01:56:04,160 --> 01:56:05,830
我有个困难
I have a problem.

1593
01:56:07,290 --> 01:56:10,880
我的伙伴，咖啡买家和他的助手
An associate of mine, a coffee buyer and his assistant,

1594
01:56:10,960 --> 01:56:13,840
到这区来出差
were on a business trip in this area.

1595
01:56:13,960 --> 01:56:16,210
他们昨天无故失踪
They unexpectedly disappeared yesterday.

1596
01:56:16,300 --> 01:56:17,800
我很担心
I'm very concerned.

1597
01:56:17,880 --> 01:56:19,340
咖啡买家
"Coffee buyer"?

1598
01:56:20,340 --> 01:56:23,140
我务必要找到他们
It's very important to me to find them.

1599
01:56:23,220 --> 01:56:26,520
咖啡买卖渐渐成为一门危险的生意
Coffee buying is becoming a very dangerous business.

1600
01:56:27,560 --> 01:56:28,640
是啊
Yes.

1601
01:56:30,310 --> 01:56:32,810
是啊，彼得·哈丁就是如此
Yes. Well, it was for Peter Hardin.

1602
01:56:35,360 --> 01:56:36,480
谁？
Who?

1603
01:56:37,190 --> 01:56:39,070
他是林度咖啡的客户
He was a client of Lindo Coffee.

1604
01:56:39,150 --> 01:56:41,110
林度咖啡有很多客户
Lindo Coffee has many clients.

1605
01:56:41,200 --> 01:56:43,820
你一定听说过他
Well, you must have heard of this one.

1606
01:56:44,330 --> 01:56:46,580
他欠你们公司一大笔钱
He owed your company a great deal of money.

1607
01:56:46,660 --> 01:56:51,670
我得问问会计部
Well, I'll have to talk to accounting about that.

1608
01:56:53,710 --> 01:56:55,670
六亿五千万…
$650 million.

1609
01:56:59,340 --> 01:57:00,680
还有零钱
And change.

1610
01:57:03,040 --> 01:57:05,060
你是来帮我…
Are you offering to help me with the...

1611
01:57:06,010 --> 01:57:07,930
收这笔帐吗？
collection of an unpaid debt?

1612
01:57:08,020 --> 01:57:09,060
不是
No.

1613
01:57:10,020 --> 01:57:11,890
那你想干嘛？
What are you offering?

1614
01:57:12,560 --> 01:57:13,770
做个交易
A trade.

1615
01:57:15,400 --> 01:57:17,360
费里斯·柯特斯出卖了你
Felix Cortez has sold you out.

1616
01:57:17,440 --> 01:57:19,930
他的下一步就是杀光你们全家
His next move is to murder you, your family,

1617
01:57:20,000 --> 01:57:21,820
然后接管整个集团
and to take over the cartel.

1618
01:57:21,900 --> 01:57:23,950
我的录音带呢？
Where is my tape recorder?

1619
01:57:30,540 --> 01:57:32,040
播来听听
Play the tape.

1620
01:58:05,950 --> 01:58:07,580
我们走吧
Let's move.

1621
01:58:37,810 --> 01:58:39,740
我给你介绍一位新朋友
I'd like you to meet my new friend.

1622
01:58:40,090 --> 01:58:41,190
莱恩博士
Dr. Ryan.

1623
01:58:41,280 --> 01:58:42,140
医生吗？
Doctor?

1624
01:58:42,700 --> 01:58:44,190
有人生病吗？
Why? Is somebody sick?

1625
01:58:58,210 --> 01:58:59,880
他要什么？
What does he want?

1626
01:59:01,960 --> 01:59:04,340
救回他的伙伴
The safe return of his associates.

1627
01:59:05,340 --> 01:59:08,890
他要用什么来换？
And what does he offer us in return?

1628
01:59:09,800 --> 01:59:10,850
你
You.

1629
01:59:18,150 --> 01:59:20,650
这家伙说的全是谎话
Whatever this man has told you is a lie.

1630
01:59:20,730 --> 01:59:22,270
他靠说谎过活
He lies for a living.

1631
01:59:22,360 --> 01:59:24,780
- 他是情报员  - 没错
- He's in the intelligence business. - Exactly.

1632
01:59:24,860 --> 01:59:27,400
你也是情报员！
You're in the intelligence business!

1633
01:59:33,660 --> 01:59:36,460
你解决了那几条小鱼
You've taken care of the little fish.

1634
01:59:36,540 --> 01:59:39,380
我来解决漏网那条大鱼
I will take care of the one that got away.

1635
01:59:39,500 --> 01:59:41,340
一旦铲除了埃斯科贝多
Once Escobedo is gone,

1636
01:59:42,210 --> 01:59:44,210
我就可以顺理成章地帮你
I will be in a position to help you.

1637
01:59:44,340 --> 01:59:48,180
所以…问题是…
So, the question is

1638
01:59:49,840 --> 01:59:51,720
我该拿你怎么办？
what am I supposed to do with you?

1639
01:59:55,560 --> 01:59:59,020
该用这根球棒把你活活打死！
Well, I guess I'm supposed to kill you with this bat!

1640
02:00:00,060 --> 02:00:03,610
你对自己的产品说太多了
I'd say you've been taking too much of your own product.

1641
02:00:05,070 --> 02:00:07,030
我也可以跟你保证…
I can also promise you...

1642
02:00:07,110 --> 02:00:08,320
站起来！
Get up!

1643
02:00:08,400 --> 02:00:11,780
破获大宗案件，你的警方可以立功…
regular quotas on major arrests that your police can take credit for.

1644
02:00:14,240 --> 02:00:16,210
破案率大增，毒品锐减
Dramatic seizures, drastic reductions,

1645
02:00:16,320 --> 02:00:18,370
再也没有无谓的暴力事件
no more violence to speak of.

1646
02:00:18,460 --> 02:00:20,460
你会取得胜利
You'll have your victory.

1647
02:00:22,460 --> 02:00:24,210
代价是什么？
In return for what?

1648
02:00:47,780 --> 02:00:49,900
切断他们的通信
Cut off their communications.

1649
02:01:04,840 --> 02:01:07,340
- 他们在哪里？  - 就在这里
- Where are they? - They're here.

1650
02:01:08,260 --> 02:01:09,420
封锁工厂！
Seal the plant!

1651
02:01:09,680 --> 02:01:11,040
美国人杀了埃内斯托！
The American killed Ernesto!

1652
02:01:11,100 --> 02:01:12,970
快点！快走！快走！
Come on! Move! Let's go!

1653
02:02:01,390 --> 02:02:03,310
小鸟呼叫变数，请回答
Bird to Variable. Over.

1654
02:02:17,070 --> 02:02:18,950
小鸟，这是变数
Bird, this is Variable.

1655
02:02:19,030 --> 02:02:20,950
你到底在哪里？
Where the hell are you?

1656
02:02:21,040 --> 02:02:26,500
我大约在村庄往南五公里处盘旋，结束
Well, I'm cruising about five clicks south of the village. Over.

1657
02:02:26,580 --> 02:02:27,610
留在那里
Stay there.

1658
02:02:27,930 --> 02:02:29,250
再连络
I'll get back to you.

1659
02:02:29,340 --> 02:02:30,710
知道了
Roger that.

1660
02:02:42,770 --> 02:02:44,350
没人
No one.

1661
02:02:44,440 --> 02:02:46,100
战俘！
The prisoners.

1662
02:03:32,070 --> 02:03:34,230
快点，各位，我们走了
Come on, guys. Let's go, son.

1663
02:03:36,400 --> 02:03:38,280
我们要回家了，兄弟
We're going home, boys.

1664
02:04:52,230 --> 02:04:54,980
到林度咖啡工厂接我们
Pick us up at the Lindo coffee factory.

1665
02:06:24,740 --> 02:06:26,660
从你的立场来看
From your point of view,

1666
02:06:26,740 --> 02:06:30,450
可以排除潜在的安全问题，不是吗？
it eliminates a potential security problem, does it not?

1667
02:06:31,410 --> 02:06:33,570
不只我可以向媒体揭发你
Not only can I expose you to the press,

1668
02:06:33,690 --> 02:06:35,290
那些士兵也可以
so can the soldiers.

1669
02:06:35,420 --> 02:06:36,880
你想冒险吗？
You want to risk it?

1670
02:06:36,960 --> 02:06:38,130
你想赌赌看吗？
You want to take your chances

1671
02:06:38,250 --> 02:06:40,090
面对法庭、国会议员
with the courts and congressional committees

1672
02:06:40,170 --> 02:06:42,170
新闻记者和全世界？
and television reporters and the world?

1673
02:06:42,260 --> 02:06:46,260
你想结束当最高统帅的政治生涯吗？
You want to end the political career of your commander-in-chief?

1674
02:07:30,800 --> 02:07:32,180
我们走吧！
Let's go!

1675
02:08:00,380 --> 02:08:03,500
快点进来！快！我们要走了！
Get your asses in here! Come on! We gotta go!

1676
02:08:07,010 --> 02:08:09,510
快点！快跑！快进来！
Come on! Run! Get your butts in here!

1677
02:08:15,720 --> 02:08:18,440
慢点！我们要等莱恩！
Hold it! We wait for Ryan!

1678
02:08:18,520 --> 02:08:20,520
什么？我们得走了！
Yeah! We're out of here!

1679
02:08:27,860 --> 02:08:29,360
快下去！
Set it down!

1680
02:08:29,450 --> 02:08:30,910
他在下面！
He's down there!

1681
02:08:43,250 --> 02:08:44,630
快点！
Come on!

1682
02:09:03,940 --> 02:09:05,480
我抓住你了！
I got you!

1683
02:09:12,570 --> 02:09:14,410
崔维斯，掩护我！
Chavez, cover me!

1684
02:09:23,920 --> 02:09:26,130
你的手！把你的手给我！
Your hand! Give me your hand!

1685
02:10:32,990 --> 02:10:35,490
总统现在要见你了
The President will see you now, sir.

1686
02:10:48,340 --> 02:10:50,880
杰克，很高兴见到你
Jack. I'm glad you're here.

1687
02:10:52,840 --> 02:10:54,380
请坐
Sit down.

1688
02:10:54,510 --> 02:10:56,760
要喝什么吗？
Can I get you anything?

1689
02:10:56,840 --> 02:10:57,930
不用了
No.

1690
02:10:59,600 --> 02:11:01,310
来吧，坐下来
Come on. Sit down.

1691
02:11:01,390 --> 02:11:03,600
我想站着，总统
I would prefer to stand, sir.

1692
02:11:06,060 --> 02:11:08,900
有一些事…
Some things have gone on here

1693
02:11:09,020 --> 02:11:11,360
…我刚刚才获悉
that I'm just becoming aware of.

1694
02:11:12,570 --> 02:11:16,240
我跟你一样，被蒙在鼓里好一阵子
I was kept in the dark, as you were, for a very long time.

1695
02:11:16,910 --> 02:11:18,870
棘手的事
Troubling things.

1696
02:11:18,950 --> 02:11:20,330
是啊
Yeah.

1697
02:11:20,410 --> 02:11:22,370
现在我们必须彻底了解
And now we have to sort them out.

1698
02:11:22,450 --> 02:11:24,830
厘清谁该负什么责任
We have to figure out who is responsible for what,

1699
02:11:24,910 --> 02:11:26,160
以及该如何解决
and what to do about it.

1700
02:11:26,250 --> 02:11:28,830
我们必须很小心地处理
And we have to do this very delicately

1701
02:11:28,920 --> 02:11:31,750
否则人们会误解
otherwise people might get the wrong idea.

1702
02:11:32,960 --> 02:11:34,550
我们必须说谎
We have to lie.

1703
02:11:36,380 --> 02:11:37,880
我有说吗？
Did I say that?

1704
02:11:38,970 --> 02:11:40,550
不，你没说
No, you didn't.

1705
02:11:41,050 --> 02:11:42,560
你很失望
You're upset.

1706
02:11:43,770 --> 02:11:44,800
我很失望
I'm upset.

1707
02:11:44,970 --> 02:11:46,560
情有可缘
Well, it's understandable.

1708
02:11:47,560 --> 02:11:50,270
介意我给你一点忠告吗？
You mind if I give you a bit of advice?

1709
02:11:50,400 --> 02:11:52,900
当然，你知道的因为你是个聪明人
Of course, you know this because you're a smart guy.

1710
02:11:53,120 --> 02:11:55,340
绝不要做重大决定
You should never make important decisions

1711
02:11:55,480 --> 02:11:56,780
在你失望的时候
while you're upset.

1712
02:11:57,320 --> 02:11:58,570
你却做了
You did,

1713
02:11:59,160 --> 02:12:02,830
美国士兵和无辜平民还因此送命
and American soldiers and innocent civilians are dead because of it.

1714
02:12:02,910 --> 02:12:04,120
我从没下令…
I never ordered any...

1715
02:12:04,240 --> 02:12:07,160
不，别跟我来这一套
No, don't even think about playing that game with me.

1716
02:12:07,250 --> 02:12:09,330
我不会任由你假装若无其事
I will not let you dishonor their memories

1717
02:12:09,420 --> 02:12:11,250
而让他们白白牺牲
by pretending you had nothing to do with it.

1718
02:12:11,330 --> 02:12:13,960
你怎么敢进来这里跟我说教？
How dare you come in here and lecture me?

1719
02:12:14,090 --> 02:12:15,170
那你怎么敢，总统？
How dare you, sir?

1720
02:12:15,260 --> 02:12:16,920
你怎么敢进到这办公室
How dare you come into this office

1721
02:12:17,010 --> 02:12:19,380
像只疯狗对我乱叫！
and bark at me like some little junkyard dog?

1722
02:12:19,470 --> 02:12:22,180
我可是美国总统！
I am the President of the United States!

1723
02:12:26,810 --> 02:12:29,440
我也很不愿意，总统
It gives me no pleasure to do it, sir.

1724
02:12:30,770 --> 02:12:33,300
身为情报局代理副局长
As Acting Deputy Director of Intelligence,

1725
02:12:33,390 --> 02:12:36,850
我有责任对监督委员会报告这件事
it is my duty to report this matter to the Senate Oversight Committee.

1726
02:12:42,990 --> 02:12:45,160
你不会那么做的
You're not gonna do that.

1727
02:12:46,830 --> 02:12:48,500
- 我不会吗？ - 不，不
- I'm not? - No, no.

1728
02:12:51,120 --> 02:12:54,170
此刻你在这场大赌局里掌握了一个筹码
You've got yourself a chip in the big game now.

1729
02:12:56,340 --> 02:12:58,210
你要把它藏好
You're gonna tuck that away.

1730
02:12:58,450 --> 02:13:02,090
留在最紧急关头时再拿出来用
You are gonna save that for a time when your own ass is on the line,

1731
02:13:02,390 --> 02:13:04,220
等你打算拿出来用时
and then you're gonna pull it out

1732
02:13:05,750 --> 02:13:07,470
我会给你兑换的
and I'm gonna cash it in for you.

1733
02:13:08,810 --> 02:13:10,140
对吧？
Right?

1734
02:13:11,980 --> 02:13:15,400
我想跟你没什么好谈的，总统
I don't think I have anything more to say to you, sir.

1735
02:13:16,860 --> 02:13:19,900
这个国家承受不起另一个丑闻，杰克
The country can't afford another scandal, Jack.

1736
02:13:21,360 --> 02:13:22,410
为了保护国家
To protect itself,

1737
02:13:22,490 --> 02:13:25,240
国家不会让诡计
it won't allow the possibility of another deception

1738
02:13:25,330 --> 02:13:27,830
影响到最高层的长官
that goes all the way to the top.

1739
02:13:27,910 --> 02:13:29,750
你会成为代罪羔羊
You'll take the blame.

1740
02:13:30,540 --> 02:13:32,200
卡特和里特也会负点责任
Cutter and Ritter will take some, too,

1741
02:13:32,290 --> 02:13:33,380
不过不会太严重
but it won't amount to much.

1742
02:13:33,500 --> 02:13:35,540
只会受到小小处罚
They'll get a slap on the wrist

1743
02:13:35,670 --> 02:13:38,710
并且在审查期间，每小时补偿两万元
and then $20,000 an hour on the lecture circuit.

1744
02:13:40,880 --> 02:13:43,680
其他的责任会推给格里尔
The rest of the blame will fall on Greer.

1745
02:13:44,930 --> 02:13:47,680
哦，对，你会拖他下水
Oh, yeah, you'll take him down with you.

1746
02:13:49,020 --> 02:13:51,730
你会毁了他的名誉
You'll destroy his reputation,

1747
02:13:51,850 --> 02:13:54,850
不过事情将会到此为止
but that's as far as it will go.

1748
02:13:55,180 --> 02:13:57,230
古老的波托马克二步舞曲，杰克
The old Potomac two-step, Jack.

1749
02:14:00,400 --> 02:14:02,820
抱歉，总统先生
I'm sorry, Mr. President.

1750
02:14:02,900 --> 02:14:04,410
我不跳舞
I don't dance.

1751
02:14:27,390 --> 02:14:28,890
莱恩，你有空吗？
Ryan, have you got a minute?

1752
02:14:29,770 --> 02:14:30,560
没有
No.

1753
02:14:32,730 --> 02:14:34,270
我们必须谈谈
We need to talk.

1754
02:14:35,440 --> 02:14:36,900
莱恩！
Ryan!

1755
02:15:01,630 --> 02:15:04,220
委员会会议正式开始
The committee will please come to order.

1756
02:15:04,300 --> 02:15:06,930
主席现在传唤约翰·莱恩博士
The chair will now call Dr. John Ryan.

1757
02:15:28,490 --> 02:15:30,120
莱恩博士，谢谢你出席
Dr. Ryan, thank you very much

1758
02:15:30,200 --> 02:15:32,580
今天的委员会会议
for appearing before the committee today.

1759
02:15:32,660 --> 02:15:34,700
谢谢你，主席
Thank you, Mr. Chairman.

1760
02:15:34,790 --> 02:15:37,500
请起立，举起你的右手
Please stand and raise your right hand.

1761
02:15:41,460 --> 02:15:42,750
你愿意郑重发誓
Do you solemnly swear

1762
02:15:42,840 --> 02:15:45,590
你在这委员会面前所说的一切
that the testimony you're about to give before this committee

1763
02:15:45,670 --> 02:15:48,640
全部都是事实，没有别的，只有事实
is the truth, the whole truth and nothing but the truth,

1764
02:15:48,720 --> 02:15:50,350
愿主保佑你吗？
so help you God?

1765
02:15:53,140 --> 02:15:54,180
我愿意
I do.

1766
02:15:56,390 --> 02:15:58,650
莱恩博士，你做了宣誓了
Dr. Ryan, you may consider yourself under oath.

1767
02:15:58,730 --> 02:16:00,360
请坐下
Please be seated.


